[metadata]

Name:Test - Macro Replay - Mind Over Matter Azami
URL:https://www.cardforge.org

Goal:Win

Turns:1

Difficulty:Rare

Description:Test puzzle for replaying a draw-discard untap loop from the commander combo list: Mind Over Matter plus Azami, Lady of Scrolls. Psychosis Crawler turns each draw into damage. Record one cycle that taps Azami to draw a card, resolves Psychosis Crawler, then discards an Island to Mind Over Matter targeting Azami to untap her. Repeat until the opponent is defeated.

